pageProduct.name: Swisse Kids Fish Oil 60 Capules
pageProduct.description:
General Information

Swisse Kids Fish Oil is a premium quality formula containing omega-3 fatty acids EPA and DHA to support cognitive function, brain health and healthy eye development.

?Sustainable source of Omega-3, which the body cannot produce so it should be obtained from the diet, to support healthy growth and development
?DHA to support healthy brain development and cognitive function
?DHA to help maintain healthy vision and support eye health
?DHA to support central nervous system development and help maintain a healthy nervous system
?Great tasting
?Natural orange flavour
?No added artifical colours or flavours
?Sustainably sourced and mercury tested
?99% sugar free
?Convenient chewable capsule

Size: 60 Pack

Warnings

Vitamin supplements should not replace a balanced diet. If symptoms persist consult your healthcare practitioner.

Ingredients

EACH CHEWABLE CAPSULE CONTAINS:
CONCENTRATED OMEGA-3 TRIGLYCERIDES - FISH 351 mg
Eicosapentaenoic acid (EPA) 35.11 mg
Docosahexaenoic acid (DHA) 165 mg

Directions

2-5 years: One capsule daily. Pierce and squeeze into water, juice or cereal.
6-12 years: One capsule daily. Chew the entire capsule or alternatively, pierce and squeeze into water, juice or cereal.
Or as directed by a healthcare professional. Do not swallow whole.

STORAGE INSTRUCTIONS

Store below 25°C in a cool, dry place. Do not use if cap seal is broken.
